process(GameData, World) - Method in interface dk.sdu.cbse.common.services.IPostProcess
This method runs once every frame, however, after the primary processes have executed, so entities and their states can be evaluated (For instance collision)
Preconditions The method process(GameData, World) runs prior to this method, as well as the method IPlugin.start(GameData, World)
Postconditions - Entity states may have been updated based on post calculations, such as collisions, health deducted etc.
